EXERCISE 03 — Install Dependencies
--------------------------------
pip install fastapi uvicorn


--------------------------------
EXERCISE 04 — Organise File Structure
--------------------------------
mkdir routes
touch main.py schema.py users.txt routes/__init__.py routes/users.py

# Initialize users.txt with an empty JSON list:
echo "[]" > users.txt



